      "seq_global": 1,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "八龙套、中军、申包胥同上。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03097003_e00002",
      "play_id": "03097003",
      "scene_id": "03097003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "点绛唇",
      "speakers": [
        "申包胥"
      ],
      "text": "奉旨出朝，地动山摇，催贡到，本奏当朝，要把狼烟扫。",
      "text_length": 25
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03097003_e00003",
      "play_id": "03097003",
      "scene_id": "03097003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "申包胥"
      ],
      "text": "奉王旨意出朝堂，各国催贡转还乡。且喜人强马又壮，一同回朝见君王。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03097003_e00004",
      "play_id": "03097003",
      "scene_id": "03097003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "申包胥"
      ],
      "text": "本爵，申包胥。奉了大王旨意，各国催贡。今已催齐，正好回朝缴旨。中军！",
      "text_length": 34
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03097003_e00005",
      "play_id": "03097003",
      "scene_id": "03097003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "中军"
      ],
      "text": "有。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03097003_e00006",
      "play_id": "03097003",
      "scene_id": "03097003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "申包胥"
      ],
      "text": "人马可齐？",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03097003_e00007",
      "play_id": "03097003",
      "scene_id": "03097003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "中军"
      ],
      "text": "俱已齐备。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03097003_e00008",
      "play_id": "03097003",
      "scene_id": "03097003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "申包胥"
      ],
      "text": "吩咐人马回朝。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03097003_e00009",
      "play_id": "03097003",
      "scene_id": "03097003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "中军"
      ],
      "text": "众将官！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03097003_e00010",
      "play_id": "03097003",
      "scene_id": "03097003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "八龙套"
      ],
      "text": "有。",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03097003_e00011",
      "play_id": "03097003",
      "scene_id": "03097003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "中军"
      ],
      "text": "人马回朝！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03097003_e00012",
      "play_id": "03097003",
      "scene_id": "03097003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "八龙套"
      ],
      "text": "啊！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03097003_e00013",
      "play_id": "03097003",
      "scene_id": "03097003_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖牌子〗。众人同下。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03097003_e00014",
      "play_id": "03097003",
      "scene_id": "03097003_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "伍员上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03097003_e00015",
      "play_id": "03097003",
      "scene_id": "03097003_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "伍员"
      ],
      "text": "且住，且喜逃出樊城，看那旁旌旗飘摇，上面写着斗大“申”字，想必是申包胥贤弟回朝。我不免勒住马头，将我满腹冤仇对他一表！",
      "text_length": 59
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03097003_e00016",
      "play_id": "03097003",
      "scene_id": "03097003_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "申包胥、八龙套、中军同上。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03097003_e00017",
      "play_id": "03097003",
      "scene_id": "03097003_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "申包胥"
      ],
      "text": "前道为何不行？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03097003_e00018",
      "play_id": "03097003",
      "scene_id": "03097003_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "八龙套"
      ],
      "text": "有人挡道。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03097003_e00019",
      "play_id": "03097003",
      "scene_id": "03097003_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "申包胥"
      ],
      "text": "人马列开。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03097003_e00020",
      "play_id": "03097003",
      "scene_id": "03097003_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "同白",
      "speakers": [
        "八龙套"
      ],
      "text": "啊！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03097003_e00021",
      "play_id": "03097003",
      "scene_id": "03097003_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "申包胥"
      ],
      "text": "兄长为何这等模样？",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03097003_e00022",
      "play_id": "03097003",
      "scene_id": "03097003_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "伍员"
      ],
      "text": "贤弟，你且听道啊！",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03097003_e00023",
      "play_id": "03097003",
      "scene_id": "03097003_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮二六板",
      "speakers": [
        "伍员"
      ],
      "text": "未曾开言泪双流，尊一声贤弟听从头：临潼会上兄为首，各国不敢强出头。双挂明辅印二口，俺子胥名儿天下游。恨平王无道贪色酒，父纳子妻理不周。我的父谏奏遭毒手，一家满门三百余口就是那鸡犬也不留。这等冤仇世少有，不杀平王誓不休。",
      "text_length": 109
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03097003_e00024",
      "play_id": "03097003",
      "scene_id": "03097003_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "申包胥"
      ],
      "text": "兄长不必眉头皱，小弟言来听从头：相国、夫人遭毒手，尽都是奸贼用计谋。你我回朝把本奏，定与你全家报冤仇。得放手来且放手，得罢休来且罢休。",
      "text_length": 67
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03097003_e00025",
      "play_id": "03097003",
      "scene_id": "03097003_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "伍员"
      ],
      "text": "贤弟说话无来由，愚兄言来听从头：昏王与我结仇扣，岂肯与他做马牛？君不正，臣逃走，父不仁来子外游。此番回朝休泄漏，念在同朝情义投。",
      "text_length": 64
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03097003_e00026",
      "play_id": "03097003",
      "scene_id": "03097003_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "申包胥"
      ],
      "text": "兄长借兵来灭楚，我为君来你为仇。今日分别三岔口，快快上马把吴投。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03097003_e00027",
      "play_id": "03097003",
      "scene_id": "03097003_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮快板",
      "speakers": [
        "伍员"
      ],
      "text": "申包胥与我把智斗，背转身来反加愁。我若是兴兵来伐楚，你为君来我为仇。贤弟请上兄叩首，感你放我往东游。辞别贤弟跨马走，",
      "text_length": 58
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03097003_e00028",
      "play_id": "03097003",
      "scene_id": "03097003_s02",
      "scene_no": 2,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "伍员上马。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03097003_e00029",
